data.value: The DataListView (bottom) is sourced from the data table above. Changes to the data table are automatically reflected in the listview. This pane also shows FormatCell events: Put 'red', 'green', 'blue', 'italic' or 'bold' in a data field to see. It also shows animated GIFs in action (though why you would ever want those, I don't know). The 'Name' column wraps text rather than truncating it. It also has custom selection colours.
